## üîπ **1. Architecture & System Design (Most Important for Senior!)**

‚úî Design scalable infrastructures
‚úî Understand trade-offs of technology
‚úî Read architecture diagrams & propose solutions

**Key Topics:**

| Area                  | Technologies & Concepts           |
| --------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| System Design         | Load Balancing, CDN, Cache Layers |
| Scalability           | Horizontal vs Vertical            |
| Patterns              | Microservices, Event-Driven, CQRS |
| API Strategies        | GraphQL, REST, gRPC               |
| Caching               | Redis, Memcached, CDN Edge        |
| Message Brokers       | Kafka, RabbitMQ, SQS              |
| Monitoring            | Prometheus, Grafana, Sentry       |
| Architecture Diagrams | C4 Model, UML                     |

